{
  "stem": "10272.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this was the, the hidden-- the hidden factor, the hidden element which helped the Nazis to do it smoothly and quickly and, and to kill the six million Jews with, with-- by, by, by complying with the order of the Gestapo to send these people without any-- without any-- suspicion that they're going to go get killed.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The project--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The project--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The project is basically based on this idea of the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did a-- I did a cable-- on cable television, on Staten Island, a program-- a one-hour program, in which-- in which participated a panel of two rabbis-- three rabbis, and the President of the Second Generation, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shelly Schore.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we debated the program, which they-- which they show-- they, they show on the television, which was including a, a monologue by myself, and a skit named which was a skit-- a, a script of a-- of a-- of a show which took place in the ghetto in Wilno during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A skit which I wrote.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not a fictional.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's based on a true story, which I took it from, from somebody who was in this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wrote about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was my writing, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I based the whole skit on a true story, which was-- which was written by-- the story was written by Chaim Lazar, who was a known Jewish Holocaust survivor and a partisan in the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was active in this-- in this project of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then I wrote also another-- I wrote a-- I, I wrote by myself a, a book, which is called This is a book which Jews, Haggadah, they call during the Passover-- in Passover Seder, Seder dinner, in which they remember the exodus of Jewish slaves from Egypt.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during that evening, the child is asking four questions their parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why do we have this dinner?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why do we have matzoh during Passover?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What does this mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What  is this remembering us?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all these questions are included in four questions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I wrote such a book, which is called in which this child, in addition to the four questions, he's asking the fifth question-- 'How could it happen?' which is not what this project of, of-- which is also a good project of Spielberg, basically, to-- the goal was what happened?",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My project is to answer the question, how could it happen?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How could  it be done?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Why did God let it happen?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Why did the Jews let themselves killed like sheep unto the slaughter?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All these unanswered questions which nobody, so far, has-- was dealing with, with these problems-- or these questions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and that's why people cannot understand up to even, so far, nobody can understand and comprehend this mind-boggling number of six million Jews got killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, I wrote--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my, my my life story, my autobiography.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I wrote it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- the Holocaust Museum in Washington, DC, wrote me-- wrote me a letter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were ready to accept my book after they had read it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They read the story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And anybody who wants to read my-- the story-- my story, they call it It's in the library of the fifth floor in the Holocaust Museum in Washington, DC.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there is my whole life story written down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a time when my wife-- we concluded-- and she finished the first chemotherapy of two years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After two years, she was in remission.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're celebrating this, this event.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We took this trip for Europe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stopped in Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stopped in Budapest, where I was walking around the places where I used to be young and before the war and during the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from there, we took a trip to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Cracow, we visited the, the synagogue over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we took-- we hired a cab.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he took us with his cab straight to Auschwitz Concentration Camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we visited the whole day in, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We took pictures.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from there, this cabbie put us to a train station in Katowice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We took a train from Katowice to Prague.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In Prague, we took a cabbie.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he took us to Karlsbad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a famous health spa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My wife, she needs this health spa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were staying there for about 10 days, about 2 weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And once my wife, when she saw I was going to sleep, she went and she picked up the phone without my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she made-- making-- she contacted the operator in, in, in, in, in the city of Nachod.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And somebody was helping her to, to, to, translate from English to Czech.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she said to this operator, please, we are in Karlsbad.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
